query: SELECT a.id, a.externalId, a.name, a.email, a.turmaId, a.trilhaId, a.consultorId, a.programId, t.name as turmaName, p.name as programName FROM alunos a LEFT JOIN turmas t ON a.turmaId = t.id LEFT JOIN programs p ON a.programId = p.id WHERE a.name LIKE '%Valci%' OR a.email LIKE '%valci%' LIMIT 5;
